thread.title_full: PLUS WATCH recensione scritta da Mac Mani Beats

author: Mac Mani Beats
title: Mac Mani Beats
text:
Plus Watch exceed my expectations.
The watch that I get is just perfect. He was always here to answer any questions.
When ordered I was asked to wait 20 days for the watch, which was fine for me. But I received just a week after, awesome!!!
This seller is really serious and is willing to satisfy you! The watch has been send via DHL and I get it in France in just 1 day !
Can't wait to do business with him again.
